ips of World War I|location=London|publisher=Ian Allan|year=1976|isbn=0-7110-0623-7}}\n*{{cite book|last=Sieche|first=Erwin|title=Kreuzer und Kreuzerprojekte der k.u.k. Kriegsmarine 1889\u20131918|language=German|trans-title=Cruisers and Cruiser Projects of the Austro-Hungarian Navy, 1889\u20131918|location=Hamburg|year=2002|isbn=978-3-8132-0766-8}}\n\n{{Austrian armored cruisers}}\n{{Austro-Hungarian Navy classes}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kaiser Karl VI, SMS}}\n[[Category:1898 ships]]\n[[Category:Cruisers of the Austro-Hungarian Navy|Kaiser Karl VI]]\n", "name_user": "Arjayay", "label": "safe", "comment": "recieved > received", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMS_Kaiser_Karl_VI"}
